description: RMF area <slider> generic slider (horizontal/vertical) with min/max/step
---

### Options
- `min <value>` — left/bottom value (default 0.0).
- `max <value>` — right/top value (default 1.0).
- `step <value>` — keyboard/button step (default 0.1).
- `vertical` / `horizontal` — orientation.
- `bar <image>` / `button <image>` / `cap <image>` — custom graphics.

